org.ops4j.peaberry.util
Class AbstractScope<S>

java.lang.Object
  org.ops4j.peaberry.util.AbstractScope<S>
All Implemented Interfaces:
ServiceScope<S>
public abstract class AbstractScope<S>
extends Object
implements ServiceScope<S>

Skeletal implementation to simplify development of ServiceScopes.

Developers only have to extend this class and provide implementations of the adding modified and removed service tracking methods. The design is loosely based on the OSGi ServiceTrackerCustomizer.
